Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:56.36,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(130,130)}踏山·世界的边际
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:15.78,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 彼方的假日·梳发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:44.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备前进 上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:45.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:55.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现敌机 准备发射主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:56.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离800
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:58.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装填手 弹种装填榴弹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:01:59.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:02.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装填完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:05.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:13.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:14.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:18.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击中目标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 通知后续部队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:22.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击毁一辆 跟上我队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:22.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:35.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击毁一辆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:37.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:39.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:41.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西娅 克劳斯来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:46.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:48.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家幸苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:03.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真变得精神了啊 守子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:07.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤都好了 还粘我们 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:09.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 这里很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:14.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:19.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么热 还那么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:22.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部送来的 麻烦签收
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:28.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:34.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的是私人信件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:37.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小彼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:40.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在 我在我在在在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:44.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄给你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:57.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈寄给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:01.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乃 你的还是那位教授同志寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:02.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授同志？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:11.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓教名授同志 赛普特州常见的姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:11.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\an8}赛普特：Spet，法语的7，另外本作的舞台赛兹(Seize)是法语中的16。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:14.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小授同志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:17.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么远的地方也有你的朋友 真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:23.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:30.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌啊 小乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还真相信了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给克劳斯送份礼物去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:47.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你·的·常·客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:57.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 司令部怎么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:30.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:36.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克…克劳斯少校阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:37.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:41.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来 谢谢泥滴管照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:51.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意 那是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:13.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 留守就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留守？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:24.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你武运昌盛 二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:30.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 明天去远足哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:33.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:37.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乃 真好啊 真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远足…菲莉西娅…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:43.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说是远足 仅仅是走路的话也太没趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:45.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不如来玩个游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:54.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛兹南部的州界 也就是与不毛大地的边界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:54.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}{\pos(416,328)}No Man's Land
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:58.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安装有旧时代的监视设备 你们应该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:02.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中三处是时候进行定期检查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:07.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们在远足的时候顺便看看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:11.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全就是任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 是远足啊远足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:17.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那东西坏了 我们也无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:24.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺克塔监视设备是完全的黑箱 无法分析
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:24.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}{\pos(396,328)}Black Box
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是远足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:29.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「武运昌盛」原来是指这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅是悠哉悠哉地走路是没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:33.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是要让你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没力气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:50.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了 这种情况要向前用力…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:03.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动…动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:05.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:07.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮不到你说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:12.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么不辜负我对你们的期待 大家真是群乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:17.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 要背重背包的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要往后倒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:27.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把背包的重量完全架到背上后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真逊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:44.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了你们 快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:46.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:58.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N那么我和菲莉西娅先绕到地图上标好的终点 等你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:01.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果觉得不行了 就吹喇叭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:05.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会去找你们…的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:09.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 这座山有野兽出没
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:13.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果遇上了可以任意应付 允许开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:18.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你们好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向右转
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向右转
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:31.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:34.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:48.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:09:59.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:07.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重 好重 好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:09.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小暮 别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:12.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越叫越觉得重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:15.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘留 还有多远
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:19.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘留 叫你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:42.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:53.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:08.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动中 没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:11.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 轻松地就找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:14.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺着这势头去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:20.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:28.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一想到它一直在这里孤单地守护着城镇…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:45.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 乃绘留 下一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:51.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:12:00.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那座山…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:41.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来想想办法搞定这个行李啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.85,0:12:42.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:48.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然队长和梨旺前辈都讨厌我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:51.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是这样 所以才这样整我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:57.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你说句话啊 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:01.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话都不说句 真不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:05.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:06.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:08.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:15.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:19.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等下 彼方？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:24.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:25.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出故障了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:35.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:50.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真凉爽 真干净啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:57.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息 无论如何都要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:02.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:03.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:13.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:18.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你干的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得玩一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:33.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘留 看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:39.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 小暮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊 真高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:47.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:50.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太没紧张感了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:53.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是远足嘛 得好好享受下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:56.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘记那个重得要死的行李了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:57.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是训练啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:00.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 菲莉西娅姐也说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该发觉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:06.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人很黑 全身都是黑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:10.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金发白肤 很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:12.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是说这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:15.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽根本不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:18.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是菲莉西娅的萌点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:19.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:20.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:23.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一定看错地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:28.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 谁来救救这对天然呆二人组
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:34.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 吃午饭啦 吃·午·饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得湿漉漉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:38.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这天气 马上就干了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:49.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粮食 没了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是野猪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:55.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我乡下也经常有菜地被践踏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:16:00.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过夏天有很多食物 一般都不会出没的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:02.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题更严重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:03.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:05.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指南针没了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:13.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗 把行李扔在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:17.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 优先到达终点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:18.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:23.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的设备是这里 河的位置在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:28.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们进入了有第二个设备的山顶所在的山头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:31.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们只要往上爬就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:34.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 无论如何也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.46,0:16:40.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:43.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么能吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:50.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杨梅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个能吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:56.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 又甜又有点酸 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:01.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫得真响
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过爬不上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:04.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:05.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应当赶路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:16.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯少校还试过三天三夜不吃不喝\N开着坦克横越沙漠 击破了敌人的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这程度 算不上什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:20.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没听说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:24.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被称为「沙漠之狼」 可厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:27.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个克劳斯叔叔他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:30.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我们继续努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:32.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我的杨梅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别发牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二个 发现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:01.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野猪？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后那个在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:20.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天都黑下来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:24.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为边详细确认方向边走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:26.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是在这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:27.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「应该」是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:33.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有指南针不能完全保证正确
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:34.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:37.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走到这里 都白费了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:39.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:43.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 这么重要的指南针 你应该放好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:47.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等啊 不要在这样的地方吵架嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:51.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底 不应该在河边悠哉悠哉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:55.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 你完全不知道什么叫紧张感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:57.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说什么远足
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:19:03.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都嘿嘿笑发大傻\N就因为你这个样子才会搞得这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗 喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:10.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:21.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:26.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 船到桥头自然直啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达终点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了 到了啊 小暮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:12.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我知道了 放开我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:13.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难受…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:16.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:33.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不毛大地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:33.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}{\pos(318,328)}No Man's Land
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:43.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是人间的边际
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:47.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:50.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:54.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务是什么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:58.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:00.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说远足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:01.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:06.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 想让你们看一看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:10.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的前辈的签名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:14.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞的少女都至少来过这里一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:21.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后都看过这个风景…看过世界的边际
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…历史吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:33.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能走一会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:37.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一处前辈们留下的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:21:59.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺…前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:02.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 那伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:02.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:05.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杨梅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:14.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:20.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:21.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:36.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 也没有白辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
